The paper proposes a method to convert monaural audio into binaural audio by leveraging visual frames, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.MM) techniques. The method also involves sound generation (cs.SD) and audio-visual source separation (cs.SI, cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.SD, cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.SI, and cs.SY, in that order.
